                                        <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
2017-骑游<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>-D3-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10445.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="千岛湖" target="_blank">千岛湖</a><br />
2017.11.04&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="上海" target="_blank">上海</a>-游骑兵&nbsp;阅读&nbsp;259<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8135610/277231633.html" data-pid="277231633">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:400px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/11/AB/wKgBEFpEWfyAN2tTAACMpW-9csc47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277231633" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">2017年，11月4号。晴天。<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10445.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="千岛湖" target="_blank">千岛湖</a>。<br />
今天继续是一个大好的晴天。早上6点半从胥口镇出发，骑没多远，太阳就在山谷中露出了笑脸，预示着美好一天的到来！从胥口到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10445.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="千岛湖" target="_blank">千岛湖</a>，我们是走302省道转208省道，这一路的路况都非常好，除了进入<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64682.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="淳安" target="_blank">淳安</a>县界，过<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11701.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="文昌" target="_blank">文昌</a>镇以后，有一段因修路半幅通行以外，全程基本都是有中央隔离带的4+2车道，新铺的柏油路面，起伏不很大的“波浪路”，再加上今天刮的是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16215.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="东北" target="_blank">东北</a>顺风，所以骑行非常顺利，除陡上坡外，速度基本都保持在20码以上。到中午11点半左右，我们已经骑了84公里路程，到达了进入<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10445.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="千岛湖" target="_blank">千岛湖</a>镇的三叉路口。<br />
<br />
在路口吃了午饭以后，考虑到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64682.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="淳安" target="_blank">淳安</a>的宾馆价格较高，我们便转向<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/31808.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="西北" target="_blank">西北</a>，跨过<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10445.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="千岛湖" target="_blank">千岛湖</a>大桥，在离桥约3公里远的山路边，找了个农庄“香约农庄”住下了（房价双人标房80元）。下午略休息后，傍晚骑车去市区转了一下，拍摄了几张<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10445.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="千岛湖" target="_blank">千岛湖</a>晚霞的照片，结束了一天的活动。<br />
<br />
今<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63015.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="天全" target="_blank">天全</a>天骑行（包括傍晚外出）共112公里。明天骑行计划：沿环<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10445.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="千岛湖" target="_blank">千岛湖</a>绿道骑行半圈至汾口镇，再骑行22公里山路到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10154.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="开化" target="_blank">开化</a>县马金镇，总骑行距离约84公里。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8135610/277231634.html" data-pid="277231634">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/11/AC/wKgBEFpEWf2AbB6xAAGdilaR7YQ44.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277231634" />
